name: Alidal
holysymbol: A crescent moon with an arrow through it.
appearance: Alidal appears as a lithe woman with skin and hair the color of the moon, covered in constantly shifting tattoos, wearing clothing made of furs.
tenets: Use every piece of your kills.
The hunt is the true expression of the self.
Self-sufficiency is an ideal to be strived for.
Do not allow others to define or control you.
parents: 3rd Generation, born of Mat'raktha and Gaian
